  description="XFPCB manufactures high-performance 12-layer PCBs for data center switches, telecom infrastructure, and server platforms. Backdrilling, hybrid Rogers/FR-4 stackups, and buried/blind via technology are standard capabilities — documented in full below."
  keywords="12 layer PCB manufacturer, server PCB, data center PCB, telecom PCB, backdrilling PCB, hybrid stackup PCB, buried via PCB, blind via PCB, Rogers FR4 hybrid, 12 layer PCB backdrilling, high speed PCB, 400G switch PCB"
  canonical="https://xfpcb.com/products/12-layer-pcb/"
  ogTitle="12 Layer PCB Manufacturer | Server, Telecom & Data Center | XFPCB"
  ogDescription="XFPCB manufactures high-performance 12-layer PCBs with backdrilling, hybrid Rogers/FR-4 stackups, and buried/blind via technology for data center, telecom, and server applications."
